   Copyright: Django Software Foundation
   URL: https://www.djangoproject.com/
   
   Django is a high-level Python web framework that encourages rapid development
   and clean, pragmatic design.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
2. pyVmomi
   Version: 9.0.0.0
   License: Apache-2.0
   Copyright: VMware, Inc.
   URL: https://github.com/vmware/pyvmomi
   
   pyVmomi is the Python SDK for the VMware vSphere API that allows you to
   manage ESX, ESXi, and vCenter.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
3. Ansible
   Version: Used via command-line execution
   License: GPL-3.0
   Copyright: Red Hat, Inc. and Ansible contributors
   URL: https://www.ansible.com/
   
   Ansible is an open-source software provisioning, configuration management,
   and application-deployment tool enabling infrastructure as code.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
4. pytz
   Version: 2025.2
   License: MIT
   Copyright: Stuart Bishop
   URL: https://pythonhosted.org/pytz/
   
   pytz brings the Olson tz database into Python, allowing accurate and
   cross-platform timezone calculations.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
5. asgiref
   Version: 3.9.2
   License: BSD-3-Clause
   Copyright: Django Software Foundation
   URL: https://github.com/django/asgiref
   
   ASGI (Asynchronous Server Gateway Interface) specification and utilities.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
6. sqlparse
   Version: 0.5.3
   License: BSD-3-Clause
   Copyright: Andi Albrecht
   URL: https://github.com/andialbrecht/sqlparse
   
   sqlparse is a non-validating SQL parser for Python. It provides support
   for parsing, splitting and formatting SQL statements.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
7. Bootstrap
   Version: 4.x (via CDN)
   License: MIT
   Copyright: Twitter, Inc. and Bootstrap contributors
   URL: https://getbootstrap.com/
   
   Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS library in the world.

