9. Font Awesome
   Version: 5.x (via CDN)
   License: Font Awesome Free License (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT)
   Copyright: Fonticons, Inc.
   URL: https://fontawesome.com/
   
   Font Awesome is the Internet's icon library and toolkit.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
10. Celery
    Version: 5.5.3
    License: BSD-3-Clause
    Copyright: Ask Solem and contributors
    URL: https://docs.celeryq.dev/
    
    Celery is a distributed task queue for Python that allows asynchronous
    execution of tasks. Used for Windows VM deployment provisioning and
    playbook execution without blocking the web interface.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
11. Redis
    Version: 6.4.0 (Python client), 6.2.19 (Server)
    License: BSD-3-Clause (Client), BSD-3-Clause (Server)
    Copyright: Redis Ltd. and contributors
    URL: https://redis.io/
    
    Redis is an in-memory data structure store used as a message broker
    for Celery task queue management and result backend.

