================================================================================
SYSTEM COMPONENTS
================================================================================

The Diaken platform consists of the following components:

1. Web Application (Django)
   - User interface for VM deployment
   - Playbook execution management
   - Inventory management
   - Scheduling system
   - Snapshot management

2. Backend Services
   - vCenter integration (pyVmomi)
   - Ansible playbook execution
   - Celery distributed task queue
   - Redis message broker
   - Cron-based scheduled tasks
   - Snapshot cleanup automation
   - Asynchronous VM deployment (Windows & Linux)

3. Database
   - SQLite (development)
   - PostgreSQL/MySQL (production ready)

4. External Dependencies
   - VMware vCenter Server
   - Ansible (system package)
   - SSH access to managed hosts

